    "location": "ITP coed sits at brookfield,aecs, kundanhalii,hopefarm, itpl,  Whitefield,. From here you can walk to Mahadevapura Junction, RMZ Infinity Old Madras Road, Amazon India Whitefield. 10 minutes to nearest tech park. No commute headache.",
